My at-risk body's hope for a #Covid19 #vaccine continues. Everyone says "get on lists." How?

Rite-Aid: We're sorry
CVS: Unavailable location
Meijer: Still waiting
Heath Dept: May at earliest
Health Provider: Silence

Yet "Got my vaccine!" stories continue to pile in. Unsettling. https://t.co/IoavJhq0U2
